title: EMC ScaleIO: Data Server Status
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors several states reported by a ScaleIO Data Server
 (SDS). The state will change to {WARN} if the maintenance mode is activated
 and to {CRIT} if the overall health is not "Normal", the connection health
 is not "connected" or the membership does not return "joined".

item:
 The SDS id

discovery:
 One service is created for each SDS.
